## 4. Training Data

> What data was used to build or train this model? How was it collected? What
> populations, geographies, languages, and time periods does it cover? What
> is missing?

[The system draws on the USDA Food Central Database for nutritional information, Local grocery store pricing APIs where available, Food bank inventory (which is updaated weekly), user interaction data which is collected through the app.
The training data for the collaborative filtering model comes from a prior 18-month pilot in Philadelphia that involved approximately 2400 households.]

